message: Add font-awesome to package.json and remove unnecessary props from button
Added nano scroll to showcase menu
Move quill as a dev dep
Move d.t.s and css as wlel
Fixed chart demos and added proper documentation
Initiated update to FullCalendar 4 and removed jQuery :)
Resizable columns for the new TreeTable
Fixed #622 - Deprecate Schedule in favor of the new FullCalendar new feature
Fixed #628 - Remove Schedule in favor of FullCalendar
Fixed #683 - Replace anchors without href with buttons
Fix #1037: QuillJS 1.3.7 to fix security vulnerability.
Refactor on showcase and update dependencies
Update primeflex and refactor tooltip demo
Revert version due to upcoming locale api
Added CSV, PDF and Excel export demo to DataTable
Set new version and update changelog files

* tooltip & fileupload - primeflex3

* charts - primeflex3

* remove primeflex2
